4Geeks Academy offers a data science and machine learning course that prepares students for a career in tech's highest-paying fields. The course is designed for beginners with no previous knowledge required. Students will learn Python, SQL, Looker (Google Data Studio), Streamlit, and Statistics. They will also create predictive models using powerful libraries like Pandas and Numpy, and explore algorithms like Close Neighbors and Decision Trees. The course covers supervised and unsupervised learning models and includes real-life case studies. Students will master the use of industry-standard tools and develop their own AI projects, following the complete lifecycle from development to deployment and maintenance. The course duration is 16 weeks, with 3 classes weekly and a maximum class size of 12 people. No previous experience is needed, and the content is available in English or Spanish. Upon completion, students receive a recognized certificate. For more information, visit the website: https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/datascience-machine-learning. stop